<p>The Google Apps for Work integration for UCS allows to easily provision Google accounts with single sign-on for users.</p>
<ul>
    <li>To use this app, a Google Apps for Work administrator account is required.</li>
    <li>To test Google Apps for Work free of charge for a month, a test account can be created at <a href="https://apps.google.com/">apps.google.com</a>.</li>
    <li>To create, modify and delete accounts, this app needs administrative access to the Google Apps for Work account. A wizard will guide you through the configuration process.</li>
</ul>
